1. *Spavali* smo duže nego obično. (We *slept* longer than usual.)
2. Oni su *spavali* u hotelu. (They *slept* in a hotel.)
3. Već smo *spavali* kada je zazvonio telefon. (We had already *fallen asleep* when the phone rang.)
4. Da li si dobro *spavao* sinoć? (Did you *sleep well* last night?)
5. Molim vas da ne *spavate* za vreme predavanja. (Please don't *fall asleep* during the lecture.)
6. *Spavajući* u šatoru, čuli smo zvukove noćne šume. (While *sleeping* in the tent, we heard the sounds of the night forest.)
7. Treba da *spavate* najmanje osam sati svake noći. (You should *sleep* for at least eight hours every night.)
8. Oni su *zaspali* od umora nakon dugog putovanja. (They *fell asleep* from exhaustion after a long journey.)
9. Mama mi je rekla da neću dobiti poklon ako ne *spavam* dovoljno. (Mom told me I won't get a gift if I don't *sleep* enough.)
10. *Spavao bih* duže, ali imam mnogo obaveza. (I would *sleep* longer, but I have a lot of obligations.)